        <div class="blob left-0 bottom-0 h-64 w-64 bg-accent-bright/40" style="animation-delay:-9s" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <div class="relative grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-normal tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Parlons de votre installation</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-lg text-white/70">Décrivez votre besoin : nous revenons avec une recommandation chiffrée, adaptée à vos références.</p>
            <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3 text-sm text-white/80">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-bright" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Étude et dimensionnement</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-bright" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Standard ou sur-mesure</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3"><svg class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-bright" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Sans engagement</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <form class="rounded-2xl glass-dark p-6 sm:p-8" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); this.querySelector('[data-ok]').classList.remove('hidden'); this.querySelector('button[type=submit]').disabled=true;">
